  "texts": [
    "The analysis of 288 student responses revealed that all five factors influence students' intentions to use ChatGPT.",
    "The last example of a student survey is the study conducted by Prather et al. [3] in 2023.",
    "They gathered 171 computing student responses from 17 countries, about half of them being in their first year of studies.",
    "Most students reported using GenAI for text or code generation, paraphrasing or summarizing text, and debugging.",
    "Some students, however, refuse to use GenAI tools due to their risks and ethical concerns."
  ],
